sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Agent as User-selected agent
    participant Skill as SKILL.md workflow
    participant CLI as Local Python CLI script
    participant FS as Local repository filesystem
    User->>Agent: Request repository inspection
    Agent->>Skill: Load inspection instructions
    Skill-->>Agent: Select script and arguments
    Agent->>CLI: Execute with local --root and --output
    Note over Agent,CLI: No application authentication or authorization layer exists
    CLI->>FS: Read repository files
    FS-->>CLI: File metadata or text
    CLI-->>Agent: JSON result or exit status
    Agent-->>User: Redacted documentation and findings
